#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1438
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "First Book of Kings"
msgstr "Primer Llibre de Reis"

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Hebrew warehouse: Port
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:953
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"Serves as a base for overseas colonization and trade. Also stores your "
"soldiers, wares and tools."
msgstr ""
"Serveix com a base per a la colonització i el comerç a l'estranger. També "
"emmagatzema els vostres soldats, mercaderies i eines."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Hebrew warehouse: Port
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:955
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"Similar to the Headquarters a Port can be attacked and destroyed by an "
"enemy. It is recommendable to send soldiers to defend it."
msgstr ""
"De manera similar a la seu, un port pot ser atacat i destruït per un enemic. "
"És recomanable enviar soldats per defensar-lo."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Hebrew production site: Branch Collector's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:964
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"'For there is hope for a tree, if it be cut down, that it will sprout again, "
"and that its shoots will not cease.'"
msgstr ""
"\"Perquè hi ha esperança per a un arbre, si es talla, que torni a brotar i "
"que els seus brots no cessin\"."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Hebrew production site: Branch Collector's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:966
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "Book of Job"
msgstr "Llibre de Job"

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Hebrew production site: Branch Collector's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:968
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"Collects fallen branches from trees in the vicinity. The trees are not "
"harmed."
msgstr ""
"Recull les branques caigudes dels arbres dels voltants. Els arbres no es fan "
"mal."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Hebrew production site: Branch Collector's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:970
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"Branches are the primary building material and fuel. The branch collector "
"needs trees nearby."
msgstr ""
"Les branques són el principal material de construcció i combustible. El "
"col·lector de branques necessita arbres a prop."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Hebrew production site: Fisher's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:977
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "'Cast your net on the right side of the boat and you will find some.'"
msgstr "'Llança la xarxa al costat dret del vaixell i en trobaràs'."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Hebrew production site: Fisher's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:979
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "Gospel of John"
msgstr "Evangeli de Joan"

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Hebrew production site: Fisher's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:981
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "Catches fish in the nearby waters."
msgstr "Agafa peixos a les aigües properes."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Hebrew production site: Fisher's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:983
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "The fisher needs water nearby to catch fish."
msgstr "El pescador necessita aigua a prop per agafar peixos."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Hebrew production site: Shepherd's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:990
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "'The Lord is my shepherd, I shall not want.'"
msgstr "\"El Senyor és el meu pastor, no em faltarà\"."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Hebrew production site: Shepherd's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:992
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "Psalm 23"
msgstr "Salm 23"

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Hebrew production site: Shepherd's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:994
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "Raises sheep for wool, meat and fur."
msgstr "Cria ovelles per a la llana, la carn i la pell."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Hebrew production site: Well
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1001
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "'Then Israel sang this song: Spring up, O well!'"
msgstr "\"Llavors Israel va cantar aquesta cançó: Spring up, oh well!\""

