#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Hebrew production site: Brick Kiln
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1040
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"Burns clay and branches into bricks, which are used as granite for "
"construction."
msgstr ""
"Crema argila i branques en maons, que s'utilitzen com a granit per a la "
"construcció."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Hebrew production site: Clearing Tent
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1047
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"'Clear the way for the people; build up the highway, remove the stones.'"
msgstr "'Deixa el camí a la gent; construïu la carretera, traieu les pedres."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Hebrew production site: Clearing Tent
#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Hebrew production site: Workshop
#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Hebrew production site: Weaponsmithy
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1049
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1186
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1208
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "Book of Isaiah"
msgstr "Llibre d'Isaïes"

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Hebrew production site: Clearing Tent
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1051
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"Clears trees to obtain logs. This allows the Hebrews to remove trees that "
"block construction."
msgstr ""
"Neteja els arbres per obtenir troncs. Això permet als hebreus eliminar els "
"arbres que bloquegen la construcció."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Hebrew production site: Spinning Mill
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1058
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "'She puts her hands to the distaff, and her hands hold the spindle.'"
msgstr ""
"\"Ella posa les mans a la roqueta, i les seves mans subjecten el fus\"."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Hebrew production site: Spinning Mill
#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Hebrew production site: Weaving Mill
